Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Master Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:50.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, Miroku and... Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:54.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Master Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:04.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made him forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I erased all his memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bring me Tetsusaiga,\NInuyasha's sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:18.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I will give Kohaku\neternal life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:27.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? What am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:39.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing... Couldn't sleep.\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:42.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,although I feel badly for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:48.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I already told you...\nhe is {\i1}not{\i0} Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku... my kid brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:54.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,could never slaughter\nan entire village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:57.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will deal with him and Naraku\nat the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He looks exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can one hate and forget\nso easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am a Demon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't fall for dirty tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I were in your position...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I probably couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks exactly the same...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he can't hate or forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha is speaking of Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be on your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We are surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Miroku!\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your Wind Tunnel\nisn't completely healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:21.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't hurry to death\nfor these small fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just have to go and\nget rid of their boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go away, vermin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You plan to fight me with\nthat level of skill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm easy! Way too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay to kill 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is Naraku's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.\NI deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:33.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:37.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father... our friends... the villagers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I killed everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why... I deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's trying to extract\nthe Sacred Jewel fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why he slashed\nhis own back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku's life is sustained{\i0} by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the fragment of the Sacred Jewel\nimbedded in his back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:18.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the fragment is removed,\NKohaku will die immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sango!\N- Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NSango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he testing me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:10.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does he really believe that\NI will take the Tetsusaiga to him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Sango!\NWhat're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no other choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only choice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My true desire...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Inuyasha?\NMiroku, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How about it, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That boy... Kohaku's blood\nis still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:02.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It still reeks of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is luring us to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Wind Tunnel is sealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the Tetsusaiga was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:13.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares!\NI still have my fists!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First, put down the Hiraikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good work, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:07.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You brought me the Tetsusaiga,\NInuyasha's sword, as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me see Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only then will I hand over\nthis sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:21.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku! Turn Kohaku back\nto his former self!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:22.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Killing me won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You should know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all the fault of\nthe Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:37.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons desiring the Sacred Jewel\nattacked your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your father's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that your brother's soul\nnow wanders...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,are all because of the\ncurse of the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You killed my father\nand comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just because you\ncovet the stupid Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you did it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:58.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,People die because of the\npower of the Sacred Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and people live because\nof its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not despise the\NSacred Jewel so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku was revived because\nof the Jewel's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:13.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The promise was to exchange\NKohaku with the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What promise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Young Lord of this castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagewaki was a fine lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He gave the slayers\nproper burials.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes... I was the one who\nordered your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagewaki Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:02.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But now, that is who I am...\nthe lord of this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!\NWhat's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:36.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My miasma is stronger\nthan any poison gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not even you, Sango,\ncan withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:54.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you serve me in this castle\nalong with Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I remember Kagewaki telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Return to the castle."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:08.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My only goal in life is to\ndestroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will avenge my father\nand comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good bye... Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- The castle!\N- Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is where Naraku\nis hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:00.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:21.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Sango!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:55.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill your brother with\nyour own hands!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:01.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then pray...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that you want to continue\nliving in this world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that you alone want to be saved!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you kill Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and you are bathed in his blood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel will glow brighter\nwith the power of the Dark.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The more sullied it{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the more beautifully\nthe Sacred Jewel glows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:34.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How could I kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:46.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}can't kill...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sango!\N- Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!\NAre you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He made her brother\ndo this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:27.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is terrible...\NHow could he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku... where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The brother who killed\nhis father... and comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His sister says she\ncannot kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She loves her brother\nmore dearly than her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:46.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I do not understand how\nthat can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:01.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}will regain consciousness\nin a little while...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,this is exactly what\nhappened with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fifty years ago, with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He tried to make Sango\nhate her brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so that she would kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:17.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then the Sacred Jewel in his back\nwould become more evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:21.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same trick he used to make\NKikyo and Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,hate each other,\nand fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:24.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:32.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo died so that the\NSacred Jewel would remain dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the same way, Sango refused\nto fight her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way Sango\nwould have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:49.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango is a kind sister\nwho loves her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:55.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A miasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:58.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Foolish mortals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drown in this sea of miasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:16.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father said you're\ngetting better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the first time\NFather praised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel sorta awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, you mustn't move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, keep still!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I gotta lot of things to\nsay to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:34.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So don't you dare die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my fault...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku has the Sacred\NJewel fragment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku!\NPrepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.06,0:18:21.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- what?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:26.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku, you are sooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This woman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is her power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With hardly any effort...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}she can purge the miasma...\nthe poison vapors...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This power belonged to Kikyo...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:39.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:43.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let you go\neven if you beg forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:52.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is none other than\NKikyo's sacred arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That means the girl is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:56.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She purged the miasma\nand located Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:05.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not let Kirara go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:11.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:14.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The castle disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a phantom castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku got away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:03.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't see any\NSacred Jewel fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NI couldn't finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:14.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without you, we'd all\nbe dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen you\nso awesome before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:24.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... we must\ndestroy Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No matter how hard it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:28.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must work together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Sango!\NYou mustn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango intends to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:41.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where in the world\ndo you intend to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NI cannot stay with you any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,we all know that you were\nbeing blackmailed by Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:50.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,over your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will betray you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as Naraku has\NKohaku under his control!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:02.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, you intend to go\nafter Naraku alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:06.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll all save your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not an opponent\none person can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay? First, we must tend\nto your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You... why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:21.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you stop yapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:23.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just stay together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Cause you fight well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:32.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? Even Inuyasha, whose\nsword you stole so easily, agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay? So no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You make me sound like\na half-wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:39.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you're just generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, do you dislike us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all my fault that this\nhappened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I may end up doing\nsomething like this again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.84,0:22:00.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poor Sango... How hard\nit must've been for her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:08.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:50.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's an herb that\nwill cure Kirara...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:53.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who was stricken with poison\nwhen she bit into Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:56.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha and I go in search\nof this herb garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:00.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and we come upon a huge\ndemon working in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:01.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He seems strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.47,0:24:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and he looks fierce...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but this demon has\nvery kind eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:12.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Jinenji, Kind Yet Sad"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.21,0:24:13.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
